        <coverage>
            <geographicCoverage>
                <geographicDescription>Surveys were carried out at fixed quadrat locations on 37 nature reserves across England. See http://publications.naturalengland.org.uk/map?category=5316639066161152. Surveys were carried out between May and September in each survey year, with repeat visits to plots undertaken at the same time of year where possible. Further site and plot information such as slope, aspect, elevation can be found here http://publications.naturalengland.org.uk/publication/4654364897050624 by using the LocationID stored for each record on the NBN Atlas.</geographicDescription>
